::Battera::

She flew high into the clouds.  She weaved in and out of the cloud banks and 
around the wind currents.  She enjoyed flying.  She thought for a moment of 
that strange red flyer she had seen earlier.  "Nah, it was a bad dream or 
something. Nothing that big can be real. Bots like that are no longer 
existing."
She flew higher.  She thought of CyberShark for a moment.
"No way,We are worlds apart. But we are on the same team." She sighed and 
headed back to the Destron base.  She flew in one of the side hatches and 
entered a small hallway.  She transformed into her bot mode and walked down 
the hall.
